rary with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","kind":"symbol"}}}